WEBVTT

00:10:59.560 --> 00:11:02.776
and smart and fast
and fights like a ninja,

00:11:02.800 --> 00:11:05.856
all four of which are true of her,

00:11:05.880 --> 00:11:07.616
it doesn't matter.

00:11:07.640 --> 00:11:10.056
She will either be ignored like Gamora

00:11:10.080 --> 00:11:12.736
or erased and replaced with a boy

00:11:12.760 --> 00:11:14.000
like Black Widow.

00:11:14.920 --> 00:11:16.576
And it's not fair.

00:11:16.600 --> 00:11:20.656
It's not fair to her and it's not fair
to your sons and daughters either.

00:11:20.680 --> 00:11:21.936
But here's the thing:

00:11:21.960 --> 00:11:25.256
I'm raising a little girl,
and she has a little tomboy in her,

00:11:25.280 --> 00:11:27.776
which by the way is
a terrible thing to call a girl.

00:11:27.800 --> 00:11:31.016
What that basically is saying is,
those traits that define you,